{"tid":435501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門氣象局稱明早會考慮改掛8號風球 (14/10)","createTime":"2017-10-14T10:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T10:48:19.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc500e2c1305d9c1703f89d856f2795f47e7062","tid":435501,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"氣象局稱明早會考慮改掛8號風球<br />\n2017.10.14 18:18<br />\n<br />\n(澳門電台消息) 本澳仍然懸掛 1號風球。氣象局表示，在未來數小時改掛3號風球，明日早上會考慮改掛 8號風球。<br />\n<br />\n傍晚 6時，強烈熱帶風暴&ldquo;卡努&rdquo;集結於本澳東南約620公里，向西北移動，大致趨向海南島至雷州半島一帶，預料本澳風力將在晚間逐漸增強，屆時將考慮改掛 3號風球。按照最新預測，&ldquo;卡努&rdquo;將繼續增強，在冬季季候風的共同影響下，廣東沿岸風力將明顯增強。<br />\n<br />\n氣象局預計&ldquo;卡努&rdquo;明天下午最接近本澳，並在本澳西南偏南約 300公里內經過。<br />\n<br />\n氣象局又稱，明天清晨及晚間潮水很可能高於內港路面約 0.5米。黃色風暴潮警告將於明日清晨5時生效。 (鄭裕華 黃偉昌)"},{"pid":"e6484e12e0f928957db0434596496bfa3acdad02","tid":435501,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"自亂陣腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d607cf4d158f1487a14fa30863f2d2b90a0fcc","tid":435501,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"加日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f5ebcecc25cf338f81b8a98d5e64b869aeb72e","tid":435501,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"香港垃圾天文台學下人哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3233647532a53b55812f1e8786c0eb4e0ef018e","tid":435501,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"今次唔屌香港狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba73e5dd2a78ba37a550a24ed39818dc7bb43b9","tid":435501,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"驚撚到"}]}